msgid "View lost opportunities"
msgstr "عرض الفرص المفقودة"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/lost_opportunities.rst:75
msgid ""
"To retrieve lost opportunities in Odoo *CRM*, open the :menuselection:`CRM "
"app`. On the main :guilabel:`Pipeline` dashboard, click into "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` bar at the top of the page, and remove all of the "
"default filters."
