"the :guilabel:`🔻(triangle pointed down)` icon to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` bar to open the drop-down menu "
"containing :guilabel:`Filters`, :guilabel:`Group By`, "
"and :guilabel:`Favorites` options, designated into respective columns."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/lost_opportunities.rst:88
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`Lost` option from the :guilabel:`Filters` section. "
"Upon selecting :guilabel:`Lost`, only the opportunities marked as `Lost` "
