msgid "Sort opportunities by lost reason"
msgstr "فرز الفرص حسب سبب الخسارة"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/lost_opportunities.rst:94
msgid ""
"To filter opportunities by a specific lost reason, click "
"the :guilabel:`🔻(triangle pointed down)` icon to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`Search...` bar again to open the drop-down menu. In addition "
"to the :guilabel:`Lost` filter, under the :guilabel:`Filters` column, "
"click :guilabel:`Add Custom Filter`, which opens an :guilabel:`Add Custom "
"Filter` pop-up window."
msgstr ""

