#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/ebay_connector/setup.rst:203
msgid ""
"To configure notifications or delete the database on a production "
"environment, navigate to the `eBay developer portal <https://"
"go.developer.ebay.com/>`_. Configure the account deletion/notification "
"settings in eBay by navigating to the `Hi [username]` at top right of "
