"in which additional addresses can be configured."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/send_quotations/different_addresses.rst:None
msgid "Add a contact/address to the contact form."
msgstr "أضف جهة اتصال/عنوانًا إلى نموذج الاتصال. "

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/send_quotations/different_addresses.rst:40
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Contact` pop-up form, start by clicking the "
